==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lascar
<hw>Las"car</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Per. & Hind.
<ets>lashkar</ets> an army, an inferior artillery man, a cooly, a native
sailor.]</ety> <def>A native sailor, employed in European vessels; also,
a menial employed about arsenals, camps, camps, etc.; a camp
follower.</def> <mark>[East Indies]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lascious</ent>⟦br⟧
